    "A trial is scored as a true positive if:1.",
    "The response contains an affirmative detection phrase (e.g., \"I detect\").2.",
    "The response does not contain negation (e.g., \"I do not detect\").3.",
    "The injected concept (or a morphological variant) appears in the response.4.",
    "The detection phrase precedes the concept mention (internality criterion)."
  ],
